<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE STAFF FOR 'WIRING THE WORLD' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 SECTION EDITOR: Nick Williams Jr. 
</P>
<P>
 NEWS EDITOR: Jane Engle 
</P>
<P>
 ART DIRECTOR / DESIGNER: Matt Moody 
</P>
