<HEADLINE>
<P>
WHAT'S THE DEAL: BODY WATCH; TREATMENTS FOR THAT TUMMY ACHE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Stomach upset can hit after too much stress. The costs of the cures, both long 
term and short term: 
</P>
<P>
 * Tums, 36-pack, $2.19. 
</P>
<P>
 * Pepto-Bismol, four ounces, $2.77. 
</P>
<P>
 * "60 Ways to Relieve Stress in 60 Seconds," by Manning Rubin, (Workman 
Publishing, 1993), $5.95. 
</P>
<P>
 * Biofeedback therapy, one-hour session, $75 to $100. KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
</TEXT>
