L.A. ARTISTS WIN $5,000 FELLOWSHIPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Los Angeles-based painters Maura Lynn Bendett, Sandow Birk and Kevin Miller, 
and L.A. video artist Jean Rasenberger are among 30 artists chosen by the 
