<HEADLINE>
<P>
DUCKS TO PLAY TWO SAN DIEGO EXHIBITIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Mighty Ducks will play eight exhibitions, including four at The Pond of 
Anaheim and two at the San Diego Sports Arena, the team announced Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 The Ducks will open their exhibition schedule against the Kings on Sept. 11 in 
San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
 The schedule (all times PDT):  
</P>
<P>
 Sept. 11 -- Kings at San Diego Sports Arena, 6:05 p.m.; 13 -- At Dallas, 5:35 
p.m.; 14 -- San Jose at Denver, 6:35 p.m.; 18 -- Vancouver at Anaheim, 6:05 
p.m.; 20 -- Boston at Anaheim, 7:35 p.m.; 21 -- Boston at San Diego Sports 
Arena, 7:35 p.m.; 23 -- Dallas at Anaheim, 7:35 p.m.; 25 -- Pittsburgh at 
Anaheim, 5:05 p.m. 
</P>
