<DOCNO> LA072694-0202 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 064175 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 26, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura East Edition 
</P>
