</P>
<P>
 Operated by the Los Angeles Unified School District Division of Adult 
Education, Career and Child Development.  
</P>
<P>
 Examples of classes: cosmetology, child care, medical careers, accounting, 
bank teller training, legal office assistant training, auto repair, 
electronics, desktop publishing, building contractor license training and 
upholstery 
</P>
<P>
