<TEXT>
<P>
 Restraining order -- A story in The Times on July 23 incorrectly reported that 
a judge had rejected a request for an injunction by county prosecutors and 
Norwalk officials to limit the activities of a gang that authorities say is 
terrorizing residents. The judge actually denied a request for a restraining 
order and set a hearing on the request for an injunction for Aug. 25. 
</P>
